TITLE: Advanced probe Integration with xargs for Batch Processing in Bash
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates using `xargs` with `probe`: extracting code snippets (`probe extract`) from a list of files generated by `probe search --files-only`, and executing `probe search` for multiple search terms provided via `echo` and standard input.
