TITLE: Using Probe AI Chat Programmatically in Node.js - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript snippet illustrates creating and using a ProbeChat instance in Node.js for programmatic access to the chat functionality, including streaming and non-streaming response options, and running within an Express or Next.js API handler. Dependencies: @buger/probe-chat npm package, correct API key for the selected provider, and optionally 'ai' package for StreamingTextResponse. Required parameters include the model, API key, (optionally) provider force, and allowed project folders. Input: user messages; Output: AI-generated responses (streaming or full).
