TITLE: Creating LangChain Tools with Probe SDK - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates integrating Probe's functionalities ('search', 'query', 'extract') into LangChain applications. It uses the 'tools.create*Tool()' functions from '@buger/probe' to create LangChain-compatible tools, which are then bound to a ChatOpenAI model using '.withTools()'. An example chat interaction using these tools is provided.
