TITLE: Example Structure of a Custom Prompt File - Prompt Format - Plain Text
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to structure a custom prompt file for ProbeChat, outlining instruction formatting, system message content, and step-by-step process guidance. The file should provide clear instructions tailored to your use case and include details for agent behavior, tool usage, XML formatting, and final result completion. There are no software dependencies, but the file must be accessible by the CLI command and adhere to ProbeChat's required prompt conventions.
