TITLE: Advanced MCP Configuration for Probe in JSON
DESCRIPTION: Advanced JSON configuration for the Probe MCP server, including environment variables for default search paths, maximum tokens, and debug mode. This provides more control over the MCP server's behavior.
SOURCE: https://github.com/buger/probe/blob/main/site/use-cases/integrating-probe-into-ai-code-editors.md#2025-04-23_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "probe": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": [
        "-y",
        "@buger/probe-mcp@latest"
      ],
      "env": {
        "PROBE_DEFAULT_PATHS": "/path/to/project1,/path/to/project2",
        "PROBE_MAX_TOKENS": "20000",
        "DEBUG": "1"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

