TITLE: Hybrid Ranking Algorithm Formula
DESCRIPTION: Formula showing how the hybrid ranking algorithm combines TF-IDF and BM25 scores with a weighting factor for improved search results.
SOURCE: https://github.com/buger/probe/blob/main/site/search-functionality.md#2025-04-23_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: bash
