TITLE: BM25 Ranking Formula
DESCRIPTION: Mathematical formula for the BM25 ranking algorithm, which improves upon TF-IDF by accounting for document length and term frequency saturation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/buger/probe/blob/main/site/search-functionality.md#2025-04-23_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
BM25(block, query) =  IDF(term) * (TF(term, block) * (k1 + 1)) / (TF(term, block) + k1 * (1 - b + b * (block_length / average_block_length)))
```

